+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: revenue DESC NULLS FIRST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |   Projection: glue.tpch.nation.n_name, sum(glue.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - glue.tpch.lineitem.l_discount) AS revenue                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |     Aggregate: groupBy=[[glue.tpch.nation.n_name]], aggr=[[sum(glue.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * (Decimal128(Some(1),20,0) - glue.tpch.lineitem.l_discount)) AS sum(glue.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - glue.tpch.lineitem.l_discount)]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |       Projection: glue.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice, glue.tpch.lineitem.l_discount, glue.tpch.nation.n_name                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |         Inner Join: glue.tpch.nation.n_regionkey = glue.tpch.region.r_regionkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |           Projection: glue.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice, glue.tpch.lineitem.l_discount, glue.tpch.nation.n_name, glue.tpch.nation.n_regionkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |             Inner Join: glue.tpch.supplier.s_nationkey = glue.tpch.nation.n_nationkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |               Projection: glue.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice, glue.tpch.lineitem.l_discount, glue.tpch.supplier.s_nationkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |                 Inner Join: glue.tpch.lineitem.l_suppkey = glue.tpch.supplier.s_suppkey, glue.tpch.customer.c_nationkey = glue.tpch.supplier.s_nationkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|               |                   Projection: glue.tpch.customer.c_nationkey, glue.tpch.lineitem.l_suppkey, glue.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice, glue.tpch.lineitem.l_discount                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                     Inner Join: glue.tpch.orders.o_orderkey = glue.tpch.lineitem.l_orderkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |                       Projection: glue.tpch.customer.c_nationkey, glue.tpch.orders.o_orderkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                         Inner Join: glue.tpch.customer.c_custkey = glue.tpch.orders.o_custkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                           TableScan: glue.tpch.customer projection=[c_custkey, c_nationkey]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |                           Projection: glue.tpch.orders.o_orderkey, glue.tpch.orders.o_custkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                             Filter: glue.tpch.orders.o_orderdate >= Date32("1994-01-01") AND glue.tpch.orders.o_orderdate < Date32("1995-01-01")                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
|               |                               TableScan: glue.tpch.orders projection=[o_orderkey, o_custkey, o_orderdate], partial_filters=[glue.tpch.orders.o_orderdate >= Date32("1994-01-01"), glue.tpch.orders.o_orderdate < Date32("1995-01-01")]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
|               |                       TableScan: glue.tpch.lineitem projection=[l_orderkey, l_suppkey, l_extendedprice, l_discount]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |                   TableScan: glue.tpch.supplier projection=[s_suppkey, s_nationkey]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |               TableScan: glue.tpch.nation projection=[n_nationkey, n_name, n_regionkey]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
|               |           Projection: glue.tpch.region.r_regionkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |             Filter: glue.tpch.region.r_name = LargeUtf8("ASIA")                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |               TableScan: glue.tpch.region projection=[r_regionkey, r_name], partial_filters=[glue.tpch.region.r_name = LargeUtf8("ASIA")]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [revenue@1 DESC]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |   SortExec: expr=[revenue@1 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[n_name@0 as n_name, sum(glue.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - glue.tpch.lineitem.l_discount)@1 as revenue]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |       AggregateExec: mode=FinalPartitioned, gby=[n_name@0 as n_name], aggr=[sum(glue.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - glue.tpch.lineitem.l_discount)]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |         CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |           RepartitionExec: partitioning=Hash([n_name@0], 32), input_partitions=32                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |             AggregateExec: mode=Partial, gby=[n_name@2 as n_name], aggr=[sum(glue.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - glue.tpch.lineitem.l_discount)]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |               CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |                 HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Inner, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(r_regionkey@0, n_regionkey@3)], projection=[l_extendedprice@1, l_discount@2, n_name@3]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |                   BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                     DataSourceExec: file_groups={1 group: [[tpch/region/region.parquet]]}, projection=[r_regionkey], file_type=parquet, predicate=r_name@1 = ASIA, pruning_predicate=r_name_null_count@2 != row_count@3 AND r_name_min@0 <= ASIA AND ASIA <= r_name_max@1, required_guarantees=[N]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |                   ProjectionExec: expr=[l_extendedprice@2 as l_extendedprice, l_discount@3 as l_discount, n_name@0 as n_name, n_regionkey@1 as n_regionkey]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |                     CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
|               |                       HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Inner, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(n_nationkey@0, s_nationkey@2)], projection=[n_name@1, n_regionkey@2, l_extendedprice@3, l_discount@4]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                         BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                           DataSourceExec: file_groups={1 group: [[tpch/nation/nation.parquet]]}, projection=[n_nationkey, n_name, n_regionkey], file_type=parquet, predicate=DynamicFilter [ empty ]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |                         ProjectionExec: expr=[l_extendedprice@1 as l_extendedprice, l_discount@2 as l_discount, s_nationkey@0 as s_nationkey]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
|               |                           CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |                             HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Inner, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(s_suppkey@0, l_suppkey@1), (s_nationkey@1, c_nationkey@0)], projection=[s_nationkey@1, l_extendedprice@4, l_discount@5]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |                               CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
